
Ranger Help for: skin
=====================

SYNTAX:      skin corpse
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   3
BASE SP:     Variable(5-50)
SKILL TYPE:  creation

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to skin the corpse of a slain foe, and create
a leather pouch from it. Usually there is some amount of meat left over
from the process that a resourceful Ranger might be able to use. The
amount of stuff that can fit in the pouch is dependent on how big of a
corpse the skin came from. The Ranger must be using a slash type weapon
in order to skin the corpse.

